<div class="container">
	<p class="introduction"><span class="tagline">The official registry of zoological nomenclature.</span> ZooBank provides a means for authors and publishers to electronically register new nomenclatural acts, and assigns unique Life Science Identifiers (<abbr title="Life Science Identifier">lsid</abbr>s) to those names. </p>
</div>


<section id="registrationForm">
	<form id="registration" class="uniForm" action="success.html" method="post" accept-charset="utf-8" name="registration">

		<div class="container">
			<h3 class="cta">Register a new name</h3>
		</div>
		
		<!-- <div id="errorMsg">
			<h3>Ooops! Your error message title</h3>
			<ol>
				<li>Error number one</li>
				<li>Error number two</li>
			</ol>
		</div> -->
		<!-- <div id="okMsg">
			<p>Looks like everything went OK! Yay!</p>
		</div> -->

		<div id="publicationTabs">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="infoMsg">
					<p>All names exist within the context of a publication. To register a name, we therefore need to know where it was (or will be) published.</p>
					<p>You may fill out the form below; save yourself time by pasting in a <abbr title="Digital Object Identifier">doi</abbr> or choosing one of your recently-entered publications.</p>
				</div>						
				<ul>
					<li><a href="#new_publication">Enter publication details</a></li>
					<li><a href="#doi_fields">Paste in a <abbr title="Digital Object Identifier">DOI</abbr></a></li>
					<li><a href="#recent_publications_fields">Choose from your recent publications</a></li>
				</ul>
						
			</div>
			<div id="new_publication"></div>
			<%=render "_doi_form.html.erb" %>
			<%=render "_recent_publications_form.html.erb" %>
		</div>
		
		<div id="nomenclaturalAct"></div>

		<fieldset class="buttons">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="buttonHolder">
					<button type="submit" class="primaryAction">Register Name</button>
				</div>
				<p><a href="step_2.html">[author disambiguation]</a> <a href="#" id="enableParentDisambiguation">[parent disambiguation]</a></p>
			</div>
		</fieldset>
	</form>
</section>

<script type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8">
	$(function(){
		$('form.uniForm').uniform();

		ZooBank.autocompleteAuthor('.authorInput');
		ZooBank.initializeAuthorList('#authorList');
		
		

	});
</script>

